{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake, ament-cmake-gtest, interactive-markers, moveit-common, moveit-core, moveit-ros-planning, rclcpp, tf2, tf2-eigen, tf2-geometry-msgs, tf2-ros }:
